Scene - Class in edu.cnm.deepdive.picturequest.model.entity
This class is an Entity class for the RoomDatabase specifically for the avaiable scenes for the 'choose' your own adventure game.
Scene() - Constructor for class edu.cnm.deepdive.picturequest.model.entity.Scene
 
SceneDao - Interface in edu.cnm.deepdive.picturequest.model.dao
a Dao interface to interact with the Scene Entity of the data base, including methods to insert one or many scenes into the data base, to get all scenes, find a specific scene based upon its id that was generated in the database and to delete scenes from the database.
